      "raw_text": "(By United Press Leased Wire)\n\n\nDECATUR, ILL.,, May 1.-Follow,\ning a bitter fight over the position\nprohibitionists should take In iii.\nnois. the state prohibition confer\nence has declared for statewide pro\nhibition in preference to any other\nplan Of action.\n\n\nTo the drafting OF resolution\nthus worded little opposition was\noffered. Originally. the resolution\ndeclared In favor Of state wide pro\nhibition, as opposed to any other\nplan."
